Privacy Policy for Tap Counter

Last updated: September 5, 2025

Tap Counter (“the App”) is developed and published by Gage Aulik (“we,” “our,” or “us”). This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use the App.

📊 Information We Collect

We do not collect, store, or share any personal information. The App does not use analytics, advertising, tracking, or third-party SDKs.

📱 How Your Data Is Used

The App stores your counter value locally on your device only.

This information never leaves your phone and is not accessible by us.

🔐 Data Security

Since no personal data is collected, there is no risk of us losing, misusing, or sharing your information. All app functionality happens entirely on your device.

👶 Children’s Privacy

The App is suitable for all ages and does not collect data from children or adults.

🌍 International Use

The App does not transfer data across borders, since no data is collected or transmitted.

📩 Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or need support, please reach out:

Email: gageaulik.56@gmail.com
